==English==
===Noun===
'''specific epithet'''
#{{biology}} The second word in the [[name]] of a [[species]], following the name of the [[genus]].  This applies only to formal names of plants, fungi and bacteria.  In formal names of animals an epithet does not occur.
::in ''Cannabis sativa'' the word ''sativa'' is a specific epithet.

